f(x,y,z) = x + 2y
x + y + z = 1
y^2 + z^2 = 4
f
 \nabla f  = (位_1)\nabla g_1 + (位_2)\nabla g_2 
 (1,2,0) = 位_1(1,1,1) + 位_2(0,2y,2z) 
z = 1 - x - y
y^2 + (1-x-y)^2 = 4
g(x,y) = y^2 + 1 + x^2 + y^2 - 2x - 2y + 2xy - 4 = 0
\nabla f = \lambda\nabla g
(1,2) = \lambda(2x-2+2y,4y-2+2x)
\dfrac{1}{2x-2+2y} = \dfrac{2}{4y-2+2x}
4y-2+2x = 4x - 4 + 4y
x = 1
y^2 + y^2 = 4
y^2 = 2
y = \pm \sqrt{2}
f_{min} = f(1,-\sqrt{2}) = 1 - 2\sqrt{2}
f_{max} = f(1,\sqrt{2}) = 1 + 2\sqrt{2}
